| Validation | Need to verify or cross-check AI-generated outputs |

## 2. New code development

**Quality bar:** A new code must meet all four criteria:
- Captures a latent or explicit interviewee need not covered by existing codes 
- Appears in ≥2 quotes or ≥2 unique interviewees (unless highly distinctive) 
- Named as a brief noun phrase (≤10 words, title case, no verbs)

**Do not create a new code if:**
- The quote fits an existing code with minor stretching
- The theme is a one-off remark with no pattern


